<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/index.min.css" defer/>
<script src="/javascripts/index.js" type="text/javascript" defer></script>
<div class="container-fluid index-container">
  <div class="row title-row center-block text-center">
    <h1 class="title-h1">Select Difficulty</h1>
    <h3 class="title-h3">(Ratings based on American curriculum)</h3>
    <hr class="title-hr">
  </div>
  <div class="row diff-row">
    <div class="col-sm-8 diff-info-col col">
      <h2 class="diff-info-h2">Easy</h2>
      <p class="diff-info-p">
        You'll probably be taught something like
        this, before or during high school
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 diff-submit-col col">
      <button class="diff-submit-btn" type="submit">Begin</button>
      <div class="diff-submit-hr"></div>
      <p class="diff-submit-p">x of y left</p>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row-cover">
      <h1 class="diff-cover-h1">Easy</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row diff-row">
    <div class="col-sm-8 diff-info-col col">
      <h2 class="diff-info-h2">Hard</h2>
      <p class="diff-info-p">
        Who needs medium? These questions are tough,
        and perhaps, most would be stumped by them
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 diff-submit-col col">
      <button class="diff-submit-btn" type="submit">Begin</button>
      <div class="diff-submit-hr"></div>
      <p class="diff-submit-p">x of y left</p>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row-cover">
      <h1 class="diff-cover-h1">Hard</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row diff-row">
    <div class="col-sm-8 diff-info-col col">
      <h2 class="diff-info-h2">Impossible?</h2>
      <p class="diff-info-p">
        Despite their historical significance,
        you're not seriously expected to know how to
        answer any of these questions, ever
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 diff-submit-col col">
      <button class="diff-submit-btn" type="submit">Begin</button>
      <div class="diff-submit-hr"></div>
      <p class="diff-submit-p">x of y left</p>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row-cover">
      <h1 class="diff-cover-h1">Impossible?</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
